SUMMARY:Studio Portrait Perfection lighting workshop w Lilli F
DESCRIPTION:The Toronto Photography Group\n## Time & Location\n\nMar 05\, 
 2026\, 7:00 PM – 10:00 PM\nRevprint Studio 205 \, 146 Thirtieth St\, Eto
 bicoke\, ON M8W 3C4\, Canada\n\n## About the event\n\n### **Studio Portrai
 t Lighting Workshop**\n\n**Date:** Thursday\, March 5th 2026\n**Time:** 7:
 00 PM – 10:00 PM\n**Instructor:** *Phil Sutherland* – Elinchrom Ambass
 ador & Executive Director\, West Toronto Photography Group\nModel Lilli F 
 - gallery of images from previous workshop\n![](https://static.wixstatic.c
 om/media/1eaf19_e3c6cd31779841cd8c1db56c456538d0~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_1686\,h
